
= SDL_SetWindowGrab =
Use this function to set a window's input grab mode.


== Syntax ==
```c++
void SDL_SetWindowGrab(SDL_Window* window,
                       SDL_bool    grabbed)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''window'''
|the window for which the input grab mode should be set
|-
|'''grabbed'''
|SDL_TRUE to grab input or SDL_FALSE to release input
|}

